<div id="review_935927528" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/935927528" />
    <a title="Lewis Weinstein" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2231715-lewis-weinstein"><img alt="Lewis Weinstein" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442501879p2/2231715.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/935927528?book_show_action=true">May 13, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lewis Weinstein" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lewis Weinstein" href="/user/show/2231715-lewis-weinstein">Lewis Weinstein</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2231715-lewis-weinstein?shelf=crime-and-thrillers">crime-and-thrillers</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer935927528" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16773850068512836216">Total immersion in the unique and fascinating culture of our Indian southwest. Strong but imperfect characters struggling with moral issues. The kind of romantic interactions I like to read about (and write about ... and live). And, oh yes, an excellent detective story. Why did I wait so long between Hillerman novels?</span>

          </span>
        </div>


