              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1769499591084811804">When Jim Chee tries to make time with his woman while on a stakeout, not only does she bring another man with her, he loses his quarry, plus a clown is murdered right under his nose. A substitute teacher is also killed.<br/><br/>There are a lot of red herrings, but Chee and Leaphorn eventually get to the bottom of things.</span>

          </span>
